e en obras que abarcan desde grandes nombres como Joyce, Huxley, Mann o Proust, hasta autores de novela policiaca o de la narrativa hispánica de los últimos años.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn Spanish, Castilian.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Mrz 2023) 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.31819/978396869424540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783968694245423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783968694245/original  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK